section_title: OTHER MATTERS: Membership of the CGE
sentences: This item was first considered on Monday, 1 December.
SBI Chair Yauvoli proposed, and parties agreed that, he would consult bilaterally with interested parties.
During the SBI closing plenary on Friday, 5 December, SBI Chair Yauvoli reported that parties were unable to reach agreement and that the sub-item will be placed on the provisional agenda of SBI 42.
